7. Broadcast is allow to use stram multiple time or multiple listen.

8. STREAM OR STREAMCONTROLLER don't have ability reach back in time andr retriev a value has already dispatch through the stream.

So we need to use behavior subjects.

----------------------------------------

Summary:

1. We use blocs instread of statefulwidget to share information around our apps.
2. We can use a bloc either as a single global instance or with a scoped instance.
3. Blocs use sinks and streams to work with information.
4. Widgets use StreamBuilders to change their contents depending on values coming through a stream
5. The RxDart libray is extremely useful in the vast majority of apps.
